definitions.definition: The bone of the forearm that extends from the elbow to the wrist on the side opposite to the thumb , corresponding to the fibula of the hind limb. Also, the corresponding bone in the forelimb of any vertebrate .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) The bone of the forearm that extends from the elbow to the wrist on the side opposite to the thumb , corresponding to the fibula of the hind limb. Also, the corresponding bone in the forelimb of any vertebrate .
